<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Sep1936"><font color="red">7 September 1936</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from John Lane to Paul L&eacute;on): We have felt all along that in view of the number of misprints which have occurred in previous editions, our edition should be as well-nigh perfect as possible, hence the referring of even the smallest queries to Mr Joyce. I may say, that  his has been a very expensive matter as far as we are concerned, as we have had to employ a man outside our own staff to supervise the work. </div>
